{"tid":2243680,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"參加x發明咗個用face ID 嘅口罩","createTime":"2020-10-15T02:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T02:44:45.000Z","uid":319228,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a229049c5792118fd57df323f17f43ca23f49afd","tid":2243680,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:25:00.000Z","msg":"用開face ID嘅都知道 Face ID而家有幾廢<br />\n<br />\niPhone 12 又堅持用FaceID<br />\n<br />\n白白廢咗個咁有用嘅功能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我參考左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFNUubF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFNUubF.jpg&h=d68f7776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkY09bF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdkY09bF.jpg&h=a9cc312c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發明咗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwisPeK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwisPeK.jpg&h=ec756244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考左耳機塞 中間通空嘅原理<br />\n<br />\n可以利用中間嘅空位 加入口罩<br />\n<br />\n用嗰陣 好似帶耳機咁 成粒塞入個鼻度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XekyKOQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXekyKOQ.gif&h=19b0eedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗安全起見 <br />\n<br />\n有參考咗鼻環嘅原理<br />\n<br />\n勾住兩粒口罩 防止塞太入/攞唔番出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TppfX7W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTppfX7W.png&h=8f2bc833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口罩正面完全睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n一定用到face ID<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/koPonAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkoPonAo.jpg&h=4f83a615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分一次性 同 可替換式<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一次性 即係gif圖嗰款 完完直接成粒噴出嚟就得<br />\n<br />\n唔使有直接接觸 減少傳播風險<br />\n<br />\n可替換式 就係只替換中間口罩 較環保<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口罩整體都係環保嘅 用量係普通口罩嘅二十分之一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家又可以用番face ID啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af76c803bcdfd4bf5046dabb02ec520684d46753","tid":2243680,"uid":299433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fda26a048dbb724887a01a3a3f164832abc2ac","tid":2243680,"uid":6061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"傻豬 口罩印自己個樣未用到囉"},{"pid":"e33052c391830e0bc501bc4a86f802cb0f766a8e","tid":2243680,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"咁個口呢"},{"pid":"b94f4d6bdb8194703ae8329a0072b1b68141b474","tid":2243680,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a229049c5792118fd57df323f17f43ca23f49afd","tid":2243680,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:25:00.000Z","msg":"用開face ID嘅都知道 Face ID而家有幾廢<br />\n<br />\niPhone 12 又堅持用FaceID<br />\n<br />\n白白廢咗個咁有用嘅功能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我參考左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFNUubF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFNUubF.jpg&h=d68f7776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkY09bF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdkY09bF.jpg&h=a9cc312c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發明咗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwisPeK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwisPeK.jpg&h=ec756244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考左耳機塞 中間通空嘅原理<br />\n<br />\n可以利用中間嘅空位 加入口罩<br />\n<br />\n用嗰陣 好似帶耳機咁 成粒塞入個鼻度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XekyKOQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXekyKOQ.gif&h=19b0eedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗安全起見 <br />\n<br />\n有參考咗鼻環嘅原理<br />\n<br />\n勾住兩粒口罩 防止塞太入/攞唔番出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https